text.header1: Kasm Open-in-Isolation hmangin links Safely leh Anonymous takin hawng rawh.
text.header2: Kasm Open in Isolation browser extension hian Workspaces isolated browser-a web link hawn theihna tur right-click menu option a pe a. Hei hian URL rinhlelh/ him lo him taka hawn emaw, i privacy vawng reng emaw chu a awlsamin a awlsam hle. Webpage hi remote workspace browser chhunga render a nih avangin, i local computer-a execute ai chuan, him tak leh hming hriat lohvin webpage nen hian i inzawm thei a ni.
